overview:
Jindo, the ever-loyal, hyper-intelligent Korean hunter, wants to make real estate fun and simple.

This real estate search platform is borne of the idea that buying, selling and renting should be both exciting and convenient. We want users (like us) who take precious time out of the day to enjoy their browsing experiences and to be able to get up-to-date information straight from the horse’s mouth. No clutter, no clogged highways. No complications. Just give me the key figures - where, how much and let me see it.

It’s free because that’s the way it should be. The web should link people, open up markets and expand horizons.

So please enjoy. We hope you find that space you’re looking for, that perfect tenant, or that buyer who will fall in love with the place you’ve filled up with so much time and energy.

This is what real estate should be. Give it a go.
